<title>Visual Connection Questions</title>
<exercise id="fs-idp203895424">
<problem id="fs-idp127568496">
<para id="fs-idp73404816"><link target-id="fig-ch25_03_06" document=""/> Which of the following statements about the moss life cycle is false?</para>
<list id="fs-idp144814112" list-type="enumerated" number-style="lower-alpha">
<item>The mature gametophyte is haploid.</item>
<item>The sporophyte produces haploid spores.</item>
