<exercise id="fs-idp117088800">
<problem id="fs-idp19742256">
<para id="fs-idp76581056">Why do mosses grow well in the Arctic tundra?</para>
<list id="fs-idp43410752" list-type="enumerated" number-style="lower-alpha">
<item>They grow better at cold temperatures.</item>
<item>They do not require moisture.</item>
<item>They do not have true roots and can grow on hard surfaces.</item>
<item>There are no herbivores in the tundra.</item>
</list>
</problem>
