<label/>
<para id="fs-idp95327328">C</para>
</solution>
</exercise><exercise id="eip-60"><problem id="eip-557">
<para id="eip-30">
A botanist travels to an area that has experienced a long, severe drought. While examining the bryophytes in the area, they notice that many are in the same life-cycle stage. Which life-cycle stage <emphasis effect="italics">should</emphasis> be the most common?
</para>
<list id="list-idp014" list-type="enumerated" number-style="lower-alpha">
<item>zygote</item>
<item>gametophyte</item>
<item>sporophyte</item>
<item>archegonium</item>
</list>
